title: Trade setup for Thursday: Top 15 things to know before the opening bell
description: Based on the OI percentage, 54 stocks were on the short-covering list. These included State Bank of India, Axis Bank, Dr Reddy’s Laboratories, Maruti Suzuki, and Hindustan Copper.
